 Internal packages: `pkg/common/types`\n488: \n489: ### Blocked By\n490: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n491: \n492: ### Blocks\n493: - AR-009 (Router HTTP 反向代理核心) - Router depends on store interface\n494: - AR-011 (Router JWT 认证与签发) - Router uses store for session management\n495: - Production deployment with session persistence\n496: \n497: ### Notes\n498: - Store operations use Redis pipelines for atomicity\n499: - Expiry index: `session:expiry` ZSET with score = `ExpiresAt.Unix()`\n500: - Last-activity index: `session:last_activity` ZSET with score = `LastActivityAt.Unix()`\n501: - Session key pattern: `session:{sessionID}`\n502: - Default provider: Redis (when STORE_TYPE is not set)\n503: - Supported providers: Redis and Valkey\n504: - Provider selection is case-insensitive\n505: - Password is required by default for both Redis and Valkey\n506: - Password requirement can be disabled via environment flags\n507: - Valkey supports comma-separated addresses for cluster mode\n508: - Valkey supports optional client flags (DisableCache, ForceSingleClient)\n509: - Singleton initialization fails fatally on connection errors\n510: - `ErrNotFound` error: `store: not found`\n511: - List operations tolerate orphan index entries\n512: - Zero limit in list operations returns `nil, nil`\n513: - `UpdateSandbox` only modifies JSON value, not indices\n514: - `StoreSandbox` validates nil sandbox and zero ExpiresAt\n515: - `UpdateSessionLastActivity` validates empty session ID and verifies existence\n516: - All Store interface methods are thread-safe\n517: - Error messages do not expose sensitive information\n\n(End of file - total 517 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-012 — 会话存储接口定义 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/store`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: S\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Update Store interface method signature\n- [ ] Update `Store` interface in `pkg/store/store.go`\n- [ ] Rename method from `GetSandbox`